sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Server
    participant D as Database
    B->>S: GET /page
    S->>D: query rows
    D-->>S: result set
    S-->>B: 200 OK
    Note over B: render DOM
    loop every 30s
        B->>S: poll updates
        S-->>B: 204 No Content
    end
